## .gitignore for CurrencyBoard
## Tells Git which files to NOT track (build outputs, IDE files, etc.)

# Build outputs
bin/
obj/

# Visual Studio files
.vs/
*.user
*.suo

# NuGet packages (restored automatically from lock file)
packages/

# Rider IDE
.idea/

# OS files
Thumbs.db
Desktop.ini
.DS_Store
